# ImageSha256

Image SHA256 checksum.

| Characteristic | Value  |
| -------------- | ------ |
| Type           | `enum` |

## Variants

### Ignored

You can pass `ignored` to skip the checksum verification.

| Characteristic | Value     |
| -------------- | --------- |
| Type           | `string`  |
| Value          | `ignored` |

### Checksum

The SHA256 checksum of the image.

*Details:*

The Sha256Hash is a 64-character hexadecimal string.

| Characteristic | Value           |
| -------------- | --------------- |
| Type           | `string`        |
| Format         | `[a-fA-F0-9]64` |
